# Block-device convenience helpers. blk_{start,finish}_plug bracket
# a batched I/O submission window (no-op for us — we don't have a
# request queue). Discard/flush fire on fsync. The "sb_blocksize"
# helpers configure the superblock's block size (mount-time).
#
